FBIS3-23195 "jptot011__l94011" JPRS-TOT-94-011-L Document Type:JPRS Document Title:Terrorism FOUO 8 March 1994 INTERNATIONAL Hijackers Seize Saudi Plane Carrying Ethiopian Deportees Hijackers Demand Fuel EA0803170594 Nairobi KBC Television Network in English 1600 GMT 8 Mar 94 EA0803170594 Nairobi KBC Television Network Language: English Article Type:BFN [Excerpt] [passage omitted] Reports say that the hijackers are demanding to be given fuel to fly to Rome, Italy. The reports add that the hijackers have released some of the crew to negotiate with authorities over their demands. Some news just in says the captain of the Saudi plane hijacked earlier this morning is being held hostage by one of the hijackers aboard the plane. Many top Kenyan security men are reported to be at the airport. The reports add that British Petroleum-Shell officials were also seen at the airport.
